'''比特币核心''' （英语：Bitcoin Core）是[[比特币|比特币]]以及其它[[加密貨幣|加密货币]]参考的[[开源|开源]][[客户端|客户端]]。最初由[[中本聪|中本聪]]以“Bitcoin”命名，后<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bitcoin.org/en/release/v0.9.0#rebranding-to-bitcoin-core|title=Bitcoin Core version 0.9.0 released|accessdate=2016-03-07|author=|date=2014-03-19|publisher=|archive-date=2015-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150227213613/https://bitcoin.org/en/release/v0.9.0#rebranding-to-bitcoin-core|dead-url=no}}</ref>改为“Bitcoin Core”。该软件会验证整个[[区块链|区块链]]曾经做过的所有交易，并默认可用于转接资金。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bitcoincore.org/en/about/|title=About – Bitcoin Core|accessdate=2016-03-07|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201140241/https://bitcoincore.org/en/about/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

